Gopi Sunder is a National Award-winning Indian musician , film score composer , programmer and singer .
He has composed music for more than 5000 advertisements , programmed music for many major composers and composed the music for nearly 50 Indian films to date .
He has composed the background score and songs for films like Flash -LRB- 2007 -RRB- , Sagar Alias Jacky Reloaded -LRB- 2009 -RRB- , Anwar -LRB- 2010 -RRB- , Ustad Hotel -LRB- 2012 -RRB- , 1983 -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , Bangalore Days -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , Charlie -LRB- 2015 -RRB- , Thozha -LRB- 2016 -RRB- , Pulimurugan -LRB- 2016 -RRB- .
He has also done the background score for Notebook -LRB- 2006 -RRB- , Big B -LRB- 2007 -RRB- , Mission 90 Days -LRB- 2007 -RRB- , Poi Solla Porom -LRB- 2008 -RRB- , Evidam Swargamanu -LRB- 2009 -RRB- , 1983 -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , Bangalore Days -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , Ennu Ninte Moideen -LRB- 2015 -RRB- , Charlie -LRB- 2015 -RRB- , Thozha -LRB- 2016 -RRB- , Devi -LRB- 2016 -RRB- , Pulimurugan '' -LRB- 2016 -RRB- .
He got his first Filmfare Award for Best Music Director in the 58th Filmfare Awards South for Anwar -LRB- 2010 -RRB- .